{"type": "article", "id": 55652, "title": "为适应多样化需求，可自定义组装的家具越来越多｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-26T22:53:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52164, "name": "MARQQA"}, {"id": 52165, "name": "PLEASE WAIT to be SEATED"}, {"id": 52166, "name": "Saba Italia"}, {"id": 52167, "name": "Luceplan"}, {"id": 52168, "name": "Mette Schelde"}, {"id": 52169, "name": "Serena Confalonieri"}, {"id": 52170, "name": "Jo Sae Bom"}, {"id": 52171, "name": "Jeong Lan"}, {"id": 52172, "name": "Daniel Rybakken"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180726232755YtKHVm7qPEGUjRB2.jpeg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Customizable Accent Furniture by MARQQA</h3><p>葡萄牙家具品牌 MARQQA 希望人们在选购家具时，能够轻松一些，少一些纠结，于是设计了一个简单易用的家具系统 LIVING，可以让用户根据自己的喜好创造自己的工作台、桌子、衣架和餐车。</p><p>它还内置了充电装置，允许用户在收纳电子产品时实现充电需求。</p><p>家具的结构、表面和饰面，有不同的选择和组合，允许用户根据自己的需要和家居风格调整部件和细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726232839Ip12zByqvE7b3AUG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807262328396bhN4iCpjEDQ9sR7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726232840DwYZ5lLP78XmqxS4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726232842FMWDlITiOpKNUebS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726232847IO70y13NuoYJV4DW.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807262328473SJqvZEPMCUnaQdc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726232847NVdX3ar2nDoxw4vq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.marqqa.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MARQQA</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Blooper Lamp by Mette Schelde for PLEASE WAIT to be SEATED</h3><p>丹麦设计家居品牌 PLEASE WAIT to be SEATED 创立于 2014 年。这盏叫 Blooper 的台灯，造型圆润可爱，使用方法也非常有趣。</p><p>设计师 Mette Schelde 将 LED 藏在中间圆盘后面，所发出的柔和灯光映射在灯罩的内部凹陷部位。而灯的开关，则是小圆盘本身，只需要旋转中间的圆盘，就能开启或关闭这盏灯，让它变亮或变暗。放在家中一角、桌面或者床边，温柔的灯光立刻让房间有了氛围感。售价 2675 丹麦克朗，<a href=\"https://pleasewaittobeseated.dk/shop/lights/blooper-table-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807262331141JpHXyYPMUWRuQ28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.519178\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233114GCPiJlQW2v9VAFdS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.987671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807262331149b5nTKLNtVy2Ur3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.969863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233114dOZz9qh6pyrGSMWH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730137\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233116F7v8hNdneql3rcVP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ring Accent Tables by Serena Confalonieri for Saba Italia </h3><p>意大利家具品牌 Saba Italia 推出 Ring Accent 系列边桌，出自米兰设计师 Serena Confalonieri 之手。灵感源自钻戒中的宝石还未切割成型时的原始样貌。玻璃桌面看起来像是固定在金属底座上，很像镶嵌钻石的戒环。</p><p>Serena Confalonieri 为桌面结构选择了四种金属桌腿，每种金属搭配特定的几何形状：铜搭配圆形烟熏玻璃，黄铜搭配正方形透明玻璃，钢搭配椭圆形海蓝色玻璃的，镍搭配八角形青铜色玻璃。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233146xdPYOILh1tvTZUp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.009375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233147up2iL8VhJPTDzy5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.982031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233147qjmP4vnYCIQ9ETrG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233147iH1DxlA7SIJKuw90.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233147u2SY7CGxZseFH0if.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.007031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233147FS4fwVgjMXmtGrWY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233148j3NiK6U1BVhkmMdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233148M8DGpAC7fNLXrt0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://sabaitalia.it/prodotto/ring/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saba Italia</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>CUP.FEE by Jo Sae Bom and Jeong Lan</h3><p>市面上零售速溶咖啡的包装袋材质主要成分是一种叫做“定向聚丙烯”的塑料，包装袋还在内层加了一层薄薄的铝。商品名称和营养信息都印在外层，而内外两层之间还夹了一层聚乙烯，从材质成分上来看，非常不环保。而且这种包装袋看上去比较廉价，还要有自己的咖啡杯才能冲泡。</p><p>鉴于这种常见咖啡袋的种种弊端，设计师 Jo Sae Bom 和Jeong Lan 运用了具有防水效果的牛皮纸制作出一种新型咖啡包装袋，CUP.FEE 便携环保咖啡包装袋。原料是水洗牛皮纸，不但环保、体积小还便于回收利用，整个包装袋还可以充当咖啡杯，便于出门在外的人士。撕下的咖啡包装封口条还能够在冲好咖啡后作为搅拌棒来使用，一举两得。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233230hBzWCM4fb7i3L0Op.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233230x0IjVRL5tHCnW7ao.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233231cB6YCuSI9MPbkyQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2014/09/22/the-better-cup/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Amisol by Daniel Rybakken for Luceplan</h3><p>创立于 1978 年的意大利灯具品牌 Luceplan，推出新品 Amisol 大型吊灯。操刀设计的是挪威设计师 Daniel Rybakken。灯具由一大片半透明白色薄膜或金属化镜膜组成，在其圆形框架内拉伸，光源将光投射到光盘上构成漫射光线或反射光线。</p><p>两根细杆将元件连接在一起，想要改变光源的方向和角度，只需改变两根支撑线的长度和连接点即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233309p7u4FPJvMSICLzxo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.379687\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233309lwqjZ1gSnuzUODkf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233310y4FMUj6OzcuC3T2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.375781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233310qBcVutzGRHnSEsQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233311ehJSr7cqX2m59tpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726233311K0FOjyIizlMSbT89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.216406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://luceplan.com/products/amisol-suspension\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luceplan</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}